             were indicted for <rs id="t18140914-124-off687" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18140914-124-off687" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18140914-124-off687" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t18140914-124-cd688" type="crimeDate">11th of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18140914-124-off687 t18140914-124-cd688"></join>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18140914-124-off689 t18140914-124-cd688"></join>, four pounds weight of bacon, value 4 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18140914-124-victim1138" type="victimName">
                     Robert 
                     Griffiths
                  <interp inst="t18140914-124-victim1138" type="surname" value="Griffiths"></interp>
